{"tid":1251535,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾偉雄：警方被動使用武力　不希望道歉變「風土病」","createTime":"2019-06-22T14:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T14:34:07.000Z","uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"406b0685a84ce3f9302f408bdf29ee0a02ae5e8f","tid":1251535,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:33:41.000Z","msg":"曾經處理2014年佔領事件的警務處前處長曾偉雄，回應上星期三金鐘警民衝突時表示，有示威者衝擊警方防線並使用武力，警方相當克制，屬於被動而不是主動使用武力。<br />\n<br />\n至於警方應否就目前警民關係緊張道歉，曾偉雄說，警方只是履行職責，不希望道歉變「風土病」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1464458-20190622.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1464458-20190622.htm&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3uCrFKAYikA6kkEaryQCE%2B8%3D&h=8b40e25a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1464458-20190622.htm&h=19190696\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1464458-20190622.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X8cv6UT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX8cv6UT.jpg&h=d9897203&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3a518ef66bf3691648c83ee6a8d05af3233808b","tid":1251535,"uid":7954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T14:34:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}